{"type": "article", "id": 26547, "title": "有着奇异水景的鱼缸", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-09T06:56:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 73, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702133420O5o49j2npvBMrPmJ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\">日本设计师<a href=\"http://misawa.ndc.co.jp/\">三澤遥</a>最近设计的 Waterscapes 系列鱼缸，是不是名副其实的“鱼住的水景房”？四四方方的透明鱼缸中放有各种奇异的造型物，以一种独特的方式模拟了水下的环境，而且都非常美观。不过，目前这些鱼缸还处于雏形阶段，三澤遥在她的<a href=\"http://www.kingstone.com.tw/book/book_page.asp?kmcode=2019600052539\">新书</a>中公开了作品的细节。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133418BOfNQvxiCE1SFw2L.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84352078\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021334185vpHm8S4K6cPDCRU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84352078\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133419QvOMBdnSHVq8ZUyC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84352078\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133419ZqUO37xpRHAPiJ5g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84352078\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}